						               													<description>Bitmax and friends spend their life playing. They do puzzles, play cooperative games, competitive games... Inside this box you'll find all of them!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;THE SEEKER  - COMPETITIVE MODE&amp;#10;FROM 8 YEARS UP// FOR 2 TO 6 PLAYERS&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player shall say the names of two characters to the player on their right who will write them down on a paper. This will be their objective.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first player shows one of the tiles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If it's in its place, you can continue picking up the tiles until you find one which isn't in its place or until you reach your objective.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If the tile is not in its place, place it facing down again and change its position with another tile on the grid.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player who gets their two characters facing up, wins the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;THE CHARACTER - COOPERATIVE MODE&amp;#10;FROM 8 YEARS UP// FOR 1 TO 6 PLAYERS&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The starting player says the name of one of the characters. This will be your objective!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first player shall show one of the outer tiles on the grid...&amp;#10;If the tile is in its place, they leave it facing up.&amp;#10;If the tile is not in its place, they leave it facing up and change its position with another tile.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game will end when you find the objective character. Each tile remaining facing down will give us one point.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;30 points Excellent&amp;#10;20 points Very good&amp;#10;10 points You should play again to train&amp;#10;&amp;#10;THE HELPER - COOPERATIVE MODE&amp;#10;FROM 6 YEARS UP  // FOR 1 TO 6 PLAYERS&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first player shall show one of the outer tiles on the grid...&amp;#10;If the tile is in its place, they leave it facing up.&amp;#10;If the tile is not in its place, they place it facing down and they can change its position with another tile facing down on the grid.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when all the tiles are in their place, well placed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;PUZZLE&amp;#10;&amp;#10;FROM 4 YEARS UP  // INDIVIDUALLY OR COLLECTIVELY&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
